<div class="Main_news_end_main__RUvv5"><div class="ArticleHead_comp_article_head__zp1Id"><a class="PressLogo_article_head_press_logo__Fm8Xa" href="http://sportalkorea.com"><img alt="스포탈코리아" height="32" src="https://mimgnews.pstatic.net/image/upload/office_logo/139/2025/07/10/logo_139_101_20250710182020.png"></a><div class="ArticleHead_article_head_title__YUNFf"><h2 class="ArticleHead_article_title__qh8GV">'충격 전망' 손흥민 LAFC 또 '찬밥 신세!'...MLS 관계자 대다수, 쏘니 메시 상대 3-0 완승에도 인터 마이애미 우승 예측</h2></div><div class="article_head_info"><div class="DateInfo_article_head_date_info__CS6Gx"><div class="DateInfo_info_item__3yQPs"><span class="DateInfo_term__ys49m">입력</span><em class="date">2026.02.24. 오후 5:40</em></div><a class="DateInfo_link_origin_article__fbZs7" href="https://www.sportalkorea.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=2025052909552999567" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">기사원문</a></div><div class="ArticleHead_function_buttons_wrap__ASggQ"><div class="ReactionButtonGroup_article_head_reaction_group__ZYqoR"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-pressed="false" class="ReactionButtonGroup_button_reaction_layer__P9PJF" type="button"><span class="icon_reaction_wrap"><span class="ReactionButtonGroup_icon_reaction__zek2B ReactionButtonGroup_type_angry__M8jU2"></span><span class="ReactionButtonGroup_icon_reaction__zek2B ReactionButtonGroup_type_like__Y5hZY"></span></span><span class="ReactionButtonGroup_count__BSL4J"><span class="blind">공감</span>345</span></button><div class="ReactionButtonGroup_reaction_layer___T2k7"><ul class="LikeitReactionList_comp_likeit_reaction_list__8LiHV LikeitReactionList_type_layer__1WF_b"><li class="LikeitReactionList_reaction_item__ByUuH LikeitReactionList_type_like__MhEsl"><button aria-pressed="false" class="LikeitReactionList_button_reaction__XBqSi" type="button"><span class="LikeitReactionList_text__EwbbK">좋아요</span><em class="LikeitReactionList_count__ys4Cl">48</em></button></li><li class="LikeitReactionList_reaction_item__ByUuH LikeitReactionList_type_sad__